feat: add OAuth2 Authorization Code server with PKCE (fl-3yj)

Standalone pkg/oauth2 package implementing OAuth2 Authorization Code
flow with PKCE support (RFC 7636) and token introspection (RFC 7662).
No faultline-specific dependencies — reusable across projects.

- Authorization Code flow with configurable consent callback
- PKCE S256 + plain support, mandatory for public clients
- Refresh token rotation with scope narrowing
- Token introspection endpoint (RFC 7662)
- Scopes: relay:read, relay:write, slack:send, account:read
- Access token TTL: 1hr, refresh token TTL: 30 days
- Pluggable Store interface with in-memory implementation
- Single-use authorization codes

